properties.name: FULL_SCREEN
properties.description: Fills the screen with the page; hides the toolbar, command bar, menu bar, and window controls.

properties.name: ZOOM_IN
properties.description: Magnifies the view to the next preset percentage.

properties.name: ZOOM_OUT
properties.description: Reduces the view to the previous preset percentage.

properties.name: FIT_PAGE
properties.description: Fits the entire page in the window.

properties.name: FIT_WIDTH
properties.description: Fits the page to the width of the window; may obscure the lower portion of the page.

properties.name: FIT_VISIBLE
properties.description: Fits the the text area of the page to the window width; obscures page margins and may obscure the lower portion of the page.

properties.name: SINGLE_PAGE
properties.description: Displays one page in the document pane at a time.

properties.name: ONE_COLUMN
properties.description: Arranges the pages in a continuous vertical column that is one page wide.

properties.name: TWO_COLUMN
properties.description: Arranges the pages side by side in a continuous vertical column that is two pages wide.
